First run! First goals are running a real route, probably without b-side skips first, and becoming more familiar with each level (and of course practicing advanced movement more and more), but I wanted to download OBS and see what it was like to submit a run. That said, blasting (mostly) through so many areas of the game that gave me so much trouble when I first bought this game two and a half weeks ago feels amazing! Can't wait to keep it pushin. Also, bathroom break at 42 minutes if anyone is wondering why the pause.
